thread.title_full: Man charged with DUI after being involved in rollover crash in C - KPTV - FOX 12

author: FOX 12 Staff
title: Man charged with DUI after being involved in rollover crash in C
text:
CLARK COUNTY, WA (KPTV) - Washington State patrols arrested a 48-year-old man on charges of driving under the influence after he was involved in a rollover crash on I-5 near Woodland late Sunday night.
Police say the driver had been traveling north and had attempted to change lanes, overcorrected, and proceeded to drive up onto the embankment before rolling his car several times.
Officers say the man was under the influence of alcohol, driving with a suspended license and was in possession of an illegal amount of Marijuana.
